7萬幾yen<br />\n佢地會有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我呢邊一年既停車場租金都係$700 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度？</blockquote><br />\n美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係來生不做香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n停慣免費，係出去玩先要比停車費。<br />\n日常生活上基本都係免費泊車，隨左去機場接居企人同朋友。"},{"pid":"dfa8aad0992b022b85c9d7ab1753ad3409fecf99","tid":415311,"uid":8717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線 渣到你地乾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢度車位好似4.幾:1,總會租得晒洗同你客氣?<br />\n所以班公居屋撚今晚好番去多謝領展(佢好多唔夠2000蚊既場都爆到不得了)"},{"pid":"3eaa7db22bdc5abfa35c4c34cf5029e93af958d0","tid":415311,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"租緊1700多層<br />\n但係幾個月hi一次<br />\n90度角轉彎<br />\n仲要窄過你條女個西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc298f70775540dca6c1278e43e9cb3fe647b3b9","tid":415311,"uid":74171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好想知同外國人講 <br />\n香港屋宛泊車一個月要6百幾美金/7萬幾yen<br />\n佢地會有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩，你泊幾多部車？"},{"pid":"6d9776a323d7a8c5dc44afb940fbcfaab101f26b","tid":415311,"uid":50442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5300泊街好過啦</blockquote><br />\n出面堆錶位長期有堆車霸住，黑警又幾乎日日嚟掃街，祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n堆錶位有啲係班地盤佬泊嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇準佢地收工嗰時就會有位<br />\n<br />\n當然都要預先同佢地打個招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ba9ba0fbb138095cab76674d0518750e7dce40","tid":415311,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"5300/30=176一日，計埋車錢+油錢+保險+牌費，至少300啦，日日的士過海仲好"},{"pid":"58995b432028798373edca853dc2e2d51857a36e","tid":415311,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係好想知同外國人講 <br />\n香港屋宛泊車一個月要6百幾美金/7萬幾yen<br />\n佢地會有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩，你泊幾多部車？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsingle family home 可以泊4-5部，如果停埋車庫的話。但好多人車庫用黎放野，只停drive way，另外就泊街。"},{"pid":"4bb3cd8019a31aeddcc74875466e96c8adf4609c","tid":415311,"uid":74259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:39:02.000Z","msg":"香港仲有幾耐會進化到單車位都要租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8b8b8d3e92103957c30db1dbe7308525eb7bea","tid":415311,"uid":3929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"香港就係乜都加 人工唔加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1faaecaf3422f70effc6ee2a25cfe2596196a7","tid":415311,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港仲有幾耐會進化到單車位都要租<img src=\"/assets/fac